title: Ep 45 - Jump Start Your New Year's Resolutions
itunes:title: Ep 45 - Jump Start Your New Year's Resolutions
description:
Today is December 2nd, that means we have 29 days to get a jump start to our New Year's Resolutions. In this episode I go over the 6 categories of resolutions and how to get a jump start on all of your goals so that you are already cranking on your goals by January 1st.
